8a2c7e89769f29282a7ddb72c7271682cd8f4f","tid":250761,"uid":27815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得係少林足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論商業、意義、搞笑、流暢都一流<br />\n<br />\n回魂夜、西遊雖然好正<br />\n之後賣碟唔錯<br />\n但唔係個個都欣賞<br />\n<br />\n少林真係顛峰之作</blockquote><br />\n兩套其實好似 各方面都好成熟 但功夫打後果d好似反而名方面既掌握都控制唔好 變左四不象咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f286710b2277b22c491f4e3bc537729c7c92d100","tid":250761,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"回魂夜死忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd46618062a1442ccedf2f1508d3a0f51109024","tid":250761,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:30:41.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打講下有咩深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f4968cfe45c037ca33601f92fd214fe37fa2bd","tid":250761,"uid":15916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T18:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打講下有咩深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔明有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246fc7a694a7755e389200bdc676109aa926250b","tid":250761,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"西遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c1d4f1f6d74778210918fe54f8b0af40f4f5d5","tid":250761,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T19:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打講下有咩深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔明有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪99後丫樓主"},{"pid":"20d9223f30ab0ca8